Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,演奏者快乐的歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,低语的黑色灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,用这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,让它破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
