Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在辉煌的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,血雨仍不停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在绝望的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,掌声仍不停止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧开始吧
