Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛在偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,祈祷的神父的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
